title: Change the way of interaction with the main circle
message:
Change the way of interaction with the main circle

1) Change from drag-and-drop on the main wheel to a simple tap.

2) Remove items being touched images and used solid color instead in
order to save memory.

title: Fix some major bugs and optimize memory usage
message:
Fix some major bugs and optimize memory usage

1) Fix when the program restarts, it keeps firing old reminders.

2) Optimize memory usage and battery draining issue.

3) Try fixing OutOfMemory exception, but fail to find a better solution
to optimize memory usage any further

4) Support some Chinese manufactures i.e. Xiaomi where they block the
permission to draw a floating window on top of other apps.

5) Add a push notification to prevent from being killed by system.

6) Finish "About" activity.

7) For users who don't have Google Voice Engine pre-installed, add a
user-friendly notice to bring to the store to install necessary Google
frameworks.

title: Use service instead of an activity
message:
Use service instead of an activity

To prevent from being killed by the system, register a background
service.
